CHAT.comment: MT is about 15.5 minutes long. Apparently Chi helped with the cooking! They talk about school a little and why Mot doesn't go to PTO meetings (doesn't want to sit there and talk to other parents). Chi has an assignment to make a musical instrument out of <household appliances>. Although they've been talking about school stuff virtually the whole time , MOT , FAT , and Chi do the classic <what did you do in school today> script near the end , which one may suspect is in part for the benefit of the tape recorder.
